title: LIVE from ‘Men Tell All’
description:
Becca and Michelle are LIVE from “Men Tell All” this week with some of the season’s most memorable men to get their thoughts on the drama-filled night. Plus, Rachel and Gabby stop by and share how they felt going into “Men Tell All,” who they were most nervous to see, and so much more. 

Then, Wells Adams stops by to discuss that wild “Bachelor in Paradise” trailer, and he drops some major tea on what goes down next season.  

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you don’t miss an episode.
